It contains the Slides and the Relevant Code for the talk which was presented by Me and Gaurav Jain (github.com/gmjain) on Introduction to Scraping in Python.

- Short Basics of HTTP
- Examples of How User Agents matter?
- What Tools you can use.
- How to scrap sale price from an item on a website.
- How to extract Facebook permissions list via a python script.
- How to write your own Google Translator API, Convert your text to any language and using Facebook API, Posting the converted text to your wall.
- How to scrap shodanhq's Results without Login.



Just clone this repo and start playing :)

Feel free to use/modify the code. 
If you have any questions regarding the talk/code, let us know.
Cheers.